text: Viva Zalata () is a 1976 Egyptian western comedy movie directed by Hassan Hafez and starring Fouad El Mohandes, Shwikar, Samir Ghanem, Tawfiq El Deken, and Hussien Fahmy. ==Other websites== * * Viva Zalata on elCinema.com Category:1976 comedy movies Category:1970s Western (genre) movies Category:Egyptian movies
